descriptions: You can download a trial version of this app to try it for 15 minutes for free.
You won’t be charged anything when this free trial ends. You can’t make in-app purchases or use add-on content during this free trial, but you’ll keep any achievements you earn.

display_long_description:
# These vehicles are… STUPID

**Speed** them up and **Slow** them down using Hand Tracking or Controllers. But be careful, these vehicles can’t stop and are full on… 

**2 Action Packed Game Modes**
- **Multiplayer - Dumb vs Dumber** - Invite a friend to 3 minutes of Madness. Highest Score Wins!

[media]
- **Arcade**  - Beat your top score, but be careful, if there’s a collision, it’s all over!

Designed to be one of the most challenging **"One More Go"** games around.

[media]
Perfect for casual players, but also offering optional challenges for the purists.
Easy Adjustable playing position  gets you right down into the action.
For a more immersive experience, try Mixed Reality Mode.

- 3-minute Multiplayer Challenge
- 8 Unique Challenging Levels – Each one with its own twist of chaos

[media]
- Cruise Control - Fill the Cruise Control Meter for a special reward

[media]
- Mixed Reality Mode
- Hand Tracking – Use your hands directly, no controllers required

[media]																							
- Cute, polished art style and animations
- Catchy original soundtrack
- Simple easy to learn gameplay
- Unique, challenging levels
- Adjustable playing position - Gets you right down into the action

[media]
- Leaderboards to compete with the world or friends
- 10 achievements for those perfectionists looking for an extra challenge
- With great risk, comes great reward. Play with “Turbo” and “Overtake” modes.

[media]
